{"type":"message","id":"fd41b257","parentId":"71df6cbb","timestamp":"2026-03-25T20:58:22.620Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is adding another principle to the framework. Let me keep track of all the constraints and principles they've provided:\n\n1. You do NOT use Claude Code\n2. No unverified Claude-Code-specific artifacts (paths, hooks, skills, MCPs, etc.)\n3. Four-factor check before adoption: utility, transferability, dependencies, adaptation needs\n4. No adoption just because it exists - everything needs conscious justification\n5. Goal is not to build autonomously as much as possible, but to guide precisely, transparently, and step-by-step\n6. Work strictly in this order and skip no phase\n7. Each phase is first treated as an architecture and integration problem, not a mere coding task\n8. Platform and system adaptation - Is this component even useful in my system?\n9. Before each implementation, explain:\n   - the purpose of the phase\n   - which parts are absolutely necessary\n   - the components to be built\n   - the benefit of each component\n   - which parts might be unnecessary for my system\n   - Minimal principle\n   - which parts are postponable\n   - which architecture decisions you need to make\n10. Prefer simple, verifiable, and extensible constructions\n\nThe phases mentioned so far:\n- Phase 1: Agent Registry, Skill-System, Hook-Engine\n- Phase 2: (unknown)\n- Phase 3: Session Store, project-based learning, Tool-/MCP-Registry\n\nI still need Phase 2 and any additional phases before we can start. Let me wait for the complete list.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Verstanden. **Minimalprinzip = einfache, überprüfbare, erweiterbare Konstruktionen bevorzugen.**\n\nIch habe jetzt den vollständigen Rahmen für jede Phase. Was noch fehlt:\n\n**Die vollständigen Phasen:**\n- Phase 1: Agent Registry, Skill-System, Hook-Engine ✓\n- Phase 2: **?**\n- Phase 3: Session Store, projektbezogenes Lernen, Tool-/MCP-Registry ✓\n- Phase 4, 5, etc.: **?**\n\nGib mir Phase 2 und alle weiteren Phasen, dann starten wir strukturiert mit Phase 1."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"kimi-k2-thinking","usage":{"input":502,"output":483,"cacheRead":17664,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18649,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774472292544}}
