{"type":"message","id":"6c4b49d2","parentId":"f75961ca","timestamp":"2026-03-25T21:03:57.229Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Gut, ich sehe mehrere Skills im Ordner:\n- example-weather\n- mission-control\n- mission-control-v2\n- secure-api-client\n- self-improving-andrew\n\nUnd einen \"skills\" Unterordner (das ist seltsam, ein Ordner namens skills im skills Ordner).\n\nIch sollte mir die Struktur eines einfachen Skills ansehen, um zu verstehen, wie OpenClaw Skills aktuell funktionieren. Lass mich example-weather oder secure-api-client ansehen, da diese vermutlich einfacher sind als mission-control.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_ho415OncNOCVhjfXyDXDmLqH","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem -Path \"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\secure-api-client\" | Select-Object Name, @{N=\"Type\";E={if($_.PSIsContainer){\"Dir\"}else{\"File\"}}}"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_wKa7jxQKcYKWmVlIN4Rpt0B5","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem -Path \"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\example-weather\" | Select-Object Name, @{N=\"Type\";E={if($_.PSIsContainer){\"Dir\"}else{\"File\"}}}"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"kimi-k2-thinking","usage":{"input":150,"output":264,"cacheRead":37120,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37534,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774472627432}}
{"type":"message","id":"25b3a607","parentId":"6c4b49d2","timestamp":"2026-03-25T21:03:57.637Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_ho415OncNOCVhjfXyDXDmLqH","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Name       Type\r\n----       ----\r\nreferences Dir \r\nscripts    Dir \r\nSKILL.md   File"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":398,"aggregated":"Name       Type\r\n----       ----\r\nreferences Dir \r\nscripts    Dir \r\nSKILL.md   File","cwd":"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774472637635}}
