{"type":"message","id":"aa09205a","parentId":"93ec2867","timestamp":"2026-03-25T21:18:51.703Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Der Nutzer möchte, dass ich Schritt 3 ausführe und die Hook-Engine erstelle. Ich sollte:\n1. registry/hooks.yaml erstellen (Konfiguration)\n2. hooks/ Ordner erstellen\n3. hooks/session-start.md Template erstellen\n4. hooks/session-end.md Template erstellen\n\nIch werde das jetzt implementieren.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Verstanden. Ich erstelle die Hook-Engine."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_4zg8xfLItiaV6M7JKD68VWjU","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path \"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\hooks\" -Force"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_8WCeM0FGoUL264I7dRNFUAxI","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Hook Registry - Phase 1 Minimal\n# Konfiguration der Hook-Engine\n# Format: YAML 1.2\n# Encoding: UTF-8\n\nversion: \"1.0\"\nlast_updated: \"2026-03-25T22:18:00+01:00\"\n\n# Hook-Engine Einstellungen\nengine:\n  enabled: true\n  max_recursion_depth: 3\n  log_hooks: true\n  fail_on_error: false\n  \n# Verfügbare Hooks mit ihren Handlern\nhooks:\n  session:start:\n    description: \"Wird beim Start einer neuen Session ausgeführt\"\n    trigger: \"session initialization\"\n    handler_file: \"hooks/session-start.md\"\n    enabled: true\n    priority: 100\n    async: false\n    \n  session:end:\n    description: \"Wird beim Ende einer Session ausgeführt\"\n    trigger: \"session termination\"\n    handler_file: \"hooks/session-end.md\"\n    enabled: true\n    priority: 100\n    async: false\n    \n  # Zukünftige Hooks (auskommentiert für spätere Phasen)\n  # message:pre:\n  #   description: \"Wird vor Verarbeitung einer Nachricht ausgeführt\"\n  #   trigger: \"message received\"\n  #   handler_file: \"hooks/message-pre.md\"\n  #   enabled: false\n  #   priority: 200\n  #   \n  # message:post:\n  #   description: \"Wird nach Verarbeitung einer Nachricht ausgeführt\"\n  #   trigger: \"message processed\"\n  #   handler_file: \"hooks/message-post.md\"\n  #   enabled: false\n  #   priority: 200\n  #   \n  # error:critical:\n  #   description: \"Wird bei kritischen Fehlern ausgeführt\"\n  #   trigger: \"critical error\"\n  #   handler_file: \"hooks/error-critical.md\"\n  #   enabled: false\n  #   priority: 999\n\n# Globale Hook-Variablen (verfügbar in allen Hooks)\nglobals:\n  workspace_path: \"C:/Users/andre/.openclaw/workspace\"\n  registry_path: \"C:/Users/andre/.openclaw/workspace/registry\"\n  agent_id: \"andrew-main\"\n  timestamp_format: \"ISO8601\"\n\n# Logging-Konfiguration\nlogging:\n  enabled: true\n  destination: \"memory/hooks.log\"\n  format: \"[{timestamp}] [{hook_id}] {status}: {message}\"\n  max_size: \"10MB\"\n  rotation: 5\n","file_path":"C:/Users/andre/.openclaw/workspace/registry/hooks.yaml"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":3452,"output":766,"cacheRead":50944,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55162,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774473515759}}
