mit Phase 2 beginnen?**\n\nAntworte mit:\n- **\"ja\"** → Starte Phase 2 Analyse (Search-first, Planner, Reviewer, Eval-Harness)\n- **\"pause\"** → Wir machen später weiter\n- **\"zeig mir erst Phase 2 Plan\"** → Ich skizziere was in Phase 2 kommt, bevor wir starten"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":1169,"output":609,"cacheRead":60672,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62450,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774473735352}}
