{"type":"message","id":"6832443e","parentId":"209c1b84","timestamp":"2026-03-25T21:34:59.989Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to go with Option 2: Hybrid approach. So:\n- Registry files (agents, skills, hooks) stay YAML (human-readable)\n- Search-Index becomes JSON (machine-optimized)\n- Plans will be Markdown (readability)\n\nI should:\n1. Convert the existing search-index.yaml to search-index.json\n2. Update references if needed\n3. Then continue with Step 2 of Phase 2 (Planner template)\n\nLet me convert the search-index to JSON format.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Verstanden. **Hybrid-Ansatz:** Search-Index wird JSON, Rest bleibt YAML.\n\nIch konvertiere den Search-Index:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_AhT3p0jTRTryekTsgtQpevV1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"{\n  \"_meta\": {\n    \"version\": \"1.0\",\n    \"last_updated\": \"2026-03-25T22:34:00+01:00\",\n    \"type\": \"keyword-index\",\n    \"generator\": \"phase2-search-index-generator\",\n    \"source_files\": [\n      \"registry/skills.yaml\",\n      \"registry/agents.yaml\",\n      \"registry/hooks.yaml\"\n    ]\n  },\n  \"stats\": {\n    \"total_entries\": 8,\n    \"skills\": 5,\n    \"agents\": 1,\n    \"hooks\": 2,\n    \"keywords_unique\": 42\n  },\n  \"entries\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"example-weather\",\n      \"type\": \"skill\",\n      \"name\": \"example-weather\",\n      \"description\": \"Fetch weather data from external APIs\",\n      \"keywords\": [\"weather\", \"forecast\", \"temperature\", \"current weather\", \"api\", \"external\", \"openweathermap\", \"location\", \"city\"],\n      \"category\": \"external-api\",\n      \"triggers\": [\"weather\", \"forecast\", \"temperature\"],\n      \"requires_env\": [\"WEATHER_API_KEY\"],\n      \"path\": \"skills/example-weather\",\n      \"priority\": 100\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"secure-api-client\",\n      \"type\": \"skill\",\n      \"name\": \"secure-api