{"type":"message","id":"2cc53694","parentId":"a1899656","timestamp":"2026-03-25T21:41:45.146Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I should create a simple Eval test file as the 4th component of Phase 2. This will be a minimal Eval-Harness.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **Schritt 3 (Phase 2) abgeschlossen — Reviewer erstellt**\n\n**Neue Dateien:**\n- `registry/review-config.yaml` (1947 B) — Review-Einstellungen\n- `hooks/review-post-execution.md` (3575 B) — Review-Hook Template\n- `registry/hooks.yaml` aktualisiert (Review-Hook hinzugefügt)\n\n**Reviewer-Features:**\n- Konfigurierbare Review-Typen (Plan, Execution, Error)\n- Integration mit `self-improving-andrew` Skill\n- Hook-basierte Auslösung\n- Qualitäts-Thresholds (80% Erfolgsrate, max \"medium\" Severity)\n- Eskalation bei wiederholten Fehlern\n\n---\n\n## SCHRITT 4 (Phase 2): Eval-Harness (Minimal)\n\n### Ziel\nEin einfacher Test für einen Skill, um das Eval-System zu demonstrieren."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_5PLizM3nxHjBw2WaOciWFqmv","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Eval Harness - Phase 2 Minimal\n# Format: YAML 1.2\n# Ein einfacher Test für den example-weather Skill\n\neval_id: \"eval-example-weather-001\"\ntitle: \"Test: example-weather Skill\"\ndescription: \"Validiert dass der Weather-Skill korrekt geladen und erkannt wird\"\ncreated_at: \"2026-03-25T22:40:00+01:00\"\nversion: \"1.0\"\n\ntarget:\n  type: \"skill\"\n  id: \"example-weather\"\n  source: \"registry/skills.yaml\"\n\n# Test-Kriterien\ncriteria:\n  - id: \"exists\"\n    description: \"Skill existiert in Registry\"\n    check: \"skills.yaml contains 'example-weather'\"\n    expected: true\n    weight: 30\n    \n  - id: \"has_description\"\n    description: \"Skill hat Beschreibung\"\n    check: \"example-weather.description is not empty\"\n    expected: true\n    weight: 20\n    \n  - id: \"has_keywords\"\n    description: \"Skill hat Keywords im Search-Index\"\n    check: \"search-index.json contains keywords for example-weather\"\n    expected: true\n    weight: 25\n    \n  - id: \"files_exist\"\n    description: \"Skill-Dateien existieren\"\n    check: \"SKILL.md exists in skills/example-weather/\"\n    expected: true\n    weight: 25\n\n# Test-Steps (manuell oder automatisiert)\nsteps:\n  - name: \"Load Registry\"\n    action: \"read registry/skills.yaml\"\n    expected: \"File loads without error\"\n    \n  - name: \"Find Skill\"\n    action: \"Parse skills list for 'example-weather'\"\n    expected: \"Skill found with metadata\"\n    \n  - name: \"Check Search Index\"\n    action: \"read registry/search-index.json\"\n    expected: \"Skill entry exists in entries array\"\n    \n  - name: \"Verify Files\"\n    action: \"List skills/example-weather/\"\n    expected: \"SKILL.md exists\"\n\n# Erfolgskriterium\nsuccess_threshold: 75  # 75% der gewichteten Kriterien müssen passen\n\n# Output\noutput:\n  format: \"markdown\"\n  location: \"memory/evals/\"\n  template: |\n    # Eval Report: {eval_id}\n    **Datum:** {timestamp}\n    **Target:** {target.id}\n    **Ergebnis:** {result}\n    **Score:** {score}%\n    \n    ## Kriterien\n    {criteria_results}\n    \n    ## Zusammenfassung\n    {summary}\n\n# Bei Fehler\non_failure:\n  action: \"log\"\n  notify: false\n  create_ticket: false\n","file_path":"C:/Users/andre/.openclaw/workspace/registry/eval-example-weather.yaml"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":1315,"output":940,"cacheRead":81152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83407,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774474886202}}
