{"type":"message","id":"01f2a91d","parentId":"b557f648","timestamp":"2026-03-25T21:42:13.079Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Perfect! Phase 2 is now complete. Let me provide a comprehensive summary to the user and ask if they want to proceed to Phase 3.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## ✅ PHASE 2 ABGESCHLOSSEN\n\n### Finale Struktur (Phase 1 + 2)\n\n```\nworkspace/\n├── registry/\n│   ├── agents.yaml              ← Phase 1\n│   ├── skills.yaml              ← Phase 1\n│   ├── hooks.yaml               ← Phase 1 (aktualisiert)\n│   ├── search-index.json        ← Phase 2 (JSON für Performance)\n│   ├── review-config.yaml       ← Phase 2 (Reviewer)\n│   ├── eval-example-weather.yaml ← Phase 2 (Eval)\n│   ├── README.md                ← Phase 1\n│   ├── VALIDATION.md            ← Phase 1\n│   └── VALIDATION-PHASE2.md     ← Phase 2\n├── hooks/\n│   ├── session-start.md         ← Phase 1\n│   ├── session-end.md           ← Phase 1\n│   └── review-post-execution.md ← Phase 2\n├── plans/\n│   ├── TEMPLATE.md              ← Phase 2\n│   └── example-phase3-prep.md   ← Phase 2\n└── AGENTS.md (aktualisiert)\n```\n\n### Zusammenfassung beider Phasen\n\n| Phase | Komponenten | Dateien | Größe | Status |\n|-------|-------------|---------|-------|--------|\n| **Phase 1** | Registry (Agents, Skills, Hooks) | 7 | ~17 KB | ✅ |\n| **Phase 2** | Search, Planner, Reviewer, Eval | 6 | ~27 KB | ✅ |\n| **Gesamt** | | **13 Dateien** | **~44 KB** | ✅ |\n\n---\n\n## PHASE 3: Session Store, projektbezogenes Lernen, Tool-/MCP-Registry\n\n**Inhalt:**\n- **Session Store:** Speicherung von Sessions über Zeit\n- **Projektbezogenes Lernen:** Lernen auf Projektebene (nicht nur global)\n- **Tool-/MCP-Registry:** Integration externer Tools und MCP-Server\n\n**Soll ich mit Phase 3 beginnen?**\n\nAntworte mit:\n- **\"ja\"** → Starte Phase 3 Analyse\n- **\"pause\"** → Wir machen später weiter\n- **\"zeig mir erst was Phase 3 ist\"** → Kurze Skizze vor dem Start"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":1145,"output":535,"cacheRead":83200,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84880,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774474921849}}
