{"type":"message","id":"beeaf91c","parentId":"9a3630c8","timestamp":"2026-03-25T21:52:27.832Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Der Benutzer hat \"ja\" gesagt. Ich soll das Install-Manifest erstellen.\n\nIch erstelle:\n1. `registry/install-manifest.yaml` - Das Manifest mit allen Komponenten aus Phase 1-3\n2. `scripts/install-check.ps1` - Ein PowerShell-Skript zum Überprüfen des Installationsstatus\n\nLass mich diese Dateien erstellen.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Verstanden. Ich erstelle das Install-Manifest und Check-Skript."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_kQec8WwR6MaefUQNviR3UWtc","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Install Manifest - Phase 4 Minimal\n# Format: YAML 1.2\n# Dieses Manifest beschreibt den Soll-Zustand des Systems\n\nmanifest:\n  version: \"1.0.0\"\n  created_at: \"2026-03-25T22:51:00+01:00\"\n  description: \"Modulares Agentisches Framework für OpenClaw\"\n  author: \"Andrew (andrew-main)\"\n  project: \"proj-modular-agent\"\n  \n  # Manifest-Metadaten\n  schema_version: \"1.0\"\n  format: \"yaml\"\n  encoding: \"UTF-8\"\n  \n  # System-Voraussetzungen\n  requirements:\n    openclaw_version: \">= 2026.3.13\"\n    platform: [\"windows\", \"linux\", \"macos\"]\n    shell: [\"powershell\", \"bash\"]\n    \n  # Installierte Komponenten\n  components:\n    # Phase 1: Registry Foundation\n    - id: \"registry-core\"\n      name: \"Core Registry\"\n      phase: 1\n      version: \"1.0\"\n      description: \"Agent, Skill und Hook Registries\"\n      required: true\n      files:\n        - path: \"registry/agents.yaml\"\n          description: \"Agent Registry\"\n          min_size: 1000\n        - path: \"registry/skills.yaml\"\n          description: \"Skill Registry\"\n          min_size: 4000\n        - path: \"registry/hooks.yaml\"\n          description: \"Hook Engine Config\"\n          min_size: 1000\n        - path: \"registry/README.md\"\n          description: \"Registry Dokumentation\"\n          optional: false\n        - path: \"registry/VALIDATION.md\"\n          description: \"Phase 1 Validierung\"\n          optional: true\n          \n    - id: \"hooks-core\"\n      name: \"Core Hooks\"\n      phase: 1\n      version: \"1.0\"\n      description: \"Session und Review Hooks\"\n      required: true\n      files:\n        - path: \"hooks/session-start.md\"\n          description: \"Session Start Hook\"\n        - path: \"hooks/session-end.md\"\n          description: \"Session End Hook\"\n        - path: \"hooks/review-post-execution.md\"\n          description: \"Review Hook\"\n          phase: 2\n          \n    # Phase 2: Cognitive Layer\n    - id: \"search-index\"\n      name: \"Search Index\"\n      phase: 2\n      version: \"1.0\"\n      description: \"Durchsuchbarer Index aller Komponenten\"\n      required: true\n      files:\n        - path: \"registry/search-index.json\"\n          description: \"Search Index (JSON)\"\n          min_size: 5000\n          format: \"json\"\n          \n    - id: \"planner\"\n      name: \"Planner System\"\n      phase: 2\n      version: \"1.0\"\n      description: \"Planung und Aufgabenzerlegung\"\n      required: true\n      directories:\n        - path: \"plans/\"\n          description: \"Plans Verzeichnis\"\n          min_files: 1\n      files:\n        - path: \"plans/TEMPLATE.md\"\n          description: \"Plan Template\"\n        - path: \"plans/example-phase3-prep.md\"\n          description: \"Beispiel Plan\"\n          optional: true\n          \n    - id: \"reviewer\"\n      name: \"Reviewer System\"\n      phase: 2\n      version: \"1.0\"\n      description: \"Qualitätsprüfung und Feedback\"\n      required: true\n      files:\n        - path: \"registry/review-config.yaml\"\n          description: \"Review Konfiguration\"\n        - path: \"registry/VALIDATION-PHASE2.md\"\n          description: \"Phase 2 Validierung\"\n          optional: true\n          \n    - id: \"eval-harness\"\n      name: \"Eval Harness\"\n      phase: 2\n      version: \"1.0\"\n      description: \"Test- und Evaluation-Framework\"\n      required: false\n      files:\n        - path: \"registry/eval-example-weather.yaml\"\n          description: \"Beispiel Eval\"\n          optional: true\n          \n    # Phase 3: Persistence & Learning\n    - id: \"session-store\"\n      name: \"Session Store\"\n      phase: 3\n      version: \"1.0\"\n      description: \"Vollständige Session-Speicherung\"\n      required: true\n      directories:\n        - path: \"memory/sessions/\"\n          description: \"Session Verzeichnis\"\n      files:\n        - path: \"memory/sessions/README.md\"\n          description: \"Session Store Doku\"\n          \n    - id: \"project-registry\"\n      name: \"Project Registry\"\n      phase: 3\n      version: \"1.0\"\n      description: \"Projekt-Verwaltung und kontextuelles Lernen\"\n      required: true\n      files:\n        - path: \"registry/projects.yaml\"\n          description: \"Project Registry\"\n      directories:\n        - path: \"memory/self-improving/projects/\"\n          description: \"Projekt-Learning Verzeichnis\"\n          \n  # Gesamt-Statistik\n  stats:\n    total_components: 8\n    required_components: 6\n    optional_components: 2\n    total_files: 18\n    total_directories: 4\n    \n  # Installation-Metadaten\n  installation:\n    method: \"manual\"\n    installed_by: \"andrew-main\"\n    installed_at: \"2026-03-25T22:51:00+01:00\"\n    verified: false\n    last_check: null\n    \n  # Update-Informationen (für zukünftige Versionen)\n  updates:\n    check_url: null  # Noch nicht implementiert\n    auto_update: false\n    \n  # Kompatibilität\n  compatibility:\n    compatible_with:\n      - \"openclaw >= 2026.3.13\"\n    conflicts_with: []\n    \n  # Notizen\n  notes: |\n    Dieses Manifest beschreibt den aktuellen Zustand des modularen\n    agentischen Frameworks nach Abschluss von Phase 1-3.\n    \n    Phase 4 Komponenten (Audit, Drift Doctor, Multi-Target) sind\n    noch nicht implementiert.\n","file_path":"C:/Users/andre/.openclaw/workspace/registry/install-manifest.yaml"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":702,"output":1630,"cacheRead":97024,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99356,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774475517345}}
