{"type":"message","id":"415bea1b","parentId":"c319e2fd","timestamp":"2026-03-25T22:04:41.433Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting! I can see:\n\n1. **Commands**: ECC has many commands like `claw.md`, `checkpoint.md`, `code-review.md`, `eval.md`, `learn.md`, `orchestrate.md`, `plan.md`, `sessions.md`, `skill-create.md`, `verify.md`, etc. - We have some of these but not all.\n\n2. **Contexts**: ECC has `dev.md`, `research.md`, `review.md` - Context management\n\n3. **Rules**: Just README.md\n\nLet me look at some specific things we might be missing:\n- Instincts (learn-eval, instinct-export, instinct-import, instinct-status)\n- More advanced commands\n- Contexts\n- Rules\n- Tests\n\nLet me explore more.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_zt8g1ZIok8LLy66850cyodNF","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:/Users/andre/Documents/Andrew Openclaw/everything-claude-code-main/commands/claw.md","limit":80}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_NgSMwRsPsho7KXKNopENMjLv","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem -Path \"C:\\Users\\andre\\Documents\\Andrew Openclaw\\everything-claude-code-main\\.claude\" -File -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object Name | Format-Table -AutoSize"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_v69DJghn3aO0T27CLuEUphXm","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem -Path \"C:\\Users\\andre\\Documents\\Andrew Openclaw\\everything-claude-code-main\\tests\" -Directory -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object Name | Format-Table -AutoSize"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":816,"output":313,"cacheRead":124928,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126057,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774476272098}}
{"type":"message","id":"8448c661","parentId":"415bea1b","timestamp":"2026-03-25T22:04:41.482Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_zt8g1ZIok8LLy66850cyodNF","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\ndescription: Start NanoClaw v2 — ECC's persistent, zero-dependency REPL with model routing, skill hot-load, branching, compaction, export, and metrics.\n---\n\n# Claw Command\n\nStart an interactive AI agent session with persistent markdown history and operational controls.\n\n## Usage\n\n```bash\nnode scripts/claw.js\n```\n\nOr via npm:\n\n```bash\nnpm run claw\n```\n\n## Environment Variables\n\n| Variable | Default | Description |\n|----------|---------|-------------|\n| `CLAW_SESSION` | `default` | Session name (alphanumeric + hyphens) |\n| `CLAW_SKILLS` | *(empty)* | Comma-separated skills loaded at startup |\n| `CLAW_MODEL` | `sonnet` | Default model for the session |\n\n## REPL Commands\n\n```text\n/help                          Show help\n/clear                         Clear current session history\n/history                       Print full conversation history\n/sessions                      List saved sessions\n/model [name]                  Show/set model\n/load <skill-name>             Hot-load a skill into context\n/branch <session-name>         Branch current session\n/search <query>                Search query across sessions\n/compact                       Compact old turns, keep recent context\n/export <md|json|txt> [path]   Export session\n/metrics                       Show session metrics\nexit                           Quit\n```\n\n## Notes\n\n- NanoClaw remains zero-dependency.\n- Sessions are stored at `~/.claude/claw/<session>.md`.\n- Compaction keeps the most recent turns and writes a compaction header.\n- Export supports markdown, JSON turns, and plain text.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774476281479}}
