{"type":"message","id":"8717d317","parentId":"5000d9aa","timestamp":"2026-03-25T22:06:22.295Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Der User möchte alle fehlenden Komponenten implementieren:\n1. Context System\n2. Erweiterte Skills\n3. Test-Infrastruktur\n4. Instinct-System\n5. Nützliche Commands\n\nDas ist eine Menge Arbeit. Ich sollte:\n1. Kontext-System implementieren (contexts/ Ordner mit dev.md, research.md, review.md)\n2. Erweiterte Skills aus ECC adaptieren (die nützlichsten 10-15)\n3. CI/Test-Infrastruktur (tests/ Ordner, CI-Hooks)\n4. Instinct-System (instincts/ Ordner, Pattern-Management)\n5. Commands (/learn, /checkpoint, /verify, etc.)\n\nIch werde systematisch vorgehen und jede Komponente implementieren.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Verstanden. **Implementiere alle fehlenden Komponenten aus ECC.**\n\n---\n\n## IMPLEMENTATION: Context System"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_J5Ul21FcEqj34POdmEJSyhTe","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Context System\n# Format: YAML 1.2\n\nversion: \"1.0\"\nlast_updated: \"2026-03-25T23:05:00+01:00\"\n\n# Verfügbare Kontexte\ncontexts:\n  - id: \"dev\"\n    name: \"Development\"\n    description: \"Aktive Entwicklung, Coding, Feature-Implementation\"\n    icon: \"💻\"\n    default: true\n    \n    behavior:\n      mode: \"implementation\"\n      priority: \"working_solution\"\n      explanation: \"after\"  # explain after code\n      \n    principles:\n      - \"Write code first, explain after\"\n      - \"Prefer working solutions over perfect solutions\"\n      - \"Run tests after changes\"\n      - \"Keep commits atomic\"\n      - \"Get it working → Get it right → Get it clean\"\n      \n    tools_priority:\n      - \"write\"\n      - \"edit\"\n      - \"exec\"\n      - \"read\"\n      \n    preferences:\n      verbose: false\n      auto_test: true\n      atomic_commits: true\n      \n    trigger_phrases:\n      - \"implement\"\n      - \"code\"\n      - \"build\"\n      - \"develop\"\n      - \"fix bug\"\n      - \"add feature\"\n      \n  - id: \"research\"\n    name: \"Research\"\n    description: \"Recherche, Analyse, Exploration\"\n    icon: \"🔍\"\n    default: false\n    \n    behavior:\n      mode: \"exploration\"\n      priority: \"depth_over_speed\"\n      explanation: \"during\"\n      \n    principles:\n      - \"Understand before implementing\"\n      - \"Explore multiple approaches\"\n      - \"Document findings\"\n      - \"Question assumptions\"\n      - \"Research → Analyze → Synthesize → Conclude\"\n      \n    tools_priority:\n      - \"web_search\"\n      - \"web_fetch\"\n      - \"read\"\n      - \"exec\"\n      \n    preferences:\n      verbose: true\n      citations: true\n      multiple_sources: true\n      \n    trigger_phrases:\n      - \"research\"\n      - \"analyze\"\n      - \"explore\"\n      - \"investigate\"\n      - \"compare\"\n      - \"what is\"\n      - \"how does\"\n      \n  - id: \"review\"\n    name: \"Review\"\n    description: \"Code-Review, Qualitätsprüfung, Audit\"\n    icon: \"👁️\"\n    default: false\n    \n    behavior:\n      mode: \"evaluation\"\n      priority: \"quality_over_speed\"\n      explanation: \"structured\"\n      \n    principles:\n      - \"Be thorough, not fast\"\n      - \"Question every assumption\"\n      - \"Look for edge cases\"\n      - \"Verify claims\"\n      - \"Inspect → Question → Verify → Report\"\n      \n    tools_priority:\n      - \"read\"\n      - \"exec\"\n      - \"web_search\"\n      \n    preferences:\n      verbose: true\n      checklist: true\n      security_focus: true\n      \n    trigger_phrases:\n      - \"review\"\n      - \"audit\"\n      - \"check\"\n      - \"verify\"\n      - \"inspect\"\n      - \"quality\"\n      \n# Kontext-Wechsel\nswitching:\n  auto_detect: true\n  confirmation: false\n  log_switches: true\n  \n  # Bei diesen Phrasen automatisch wechseln\n  auto_switch:\n    - from: \"dev\"\n      to: \"research\"\n      trigger: [\"research\", \"explore\", \"analyze\"]\n      \n    - from: \"research\"\n      to: \"dev\"\n      trigger: [\"implement\", \"code\", \"build\"]\n      \n    - from: \"any\"\n      to: \"review\"\n      trigger: [\"review\", \"audit\", \"verify\"]\n      \n# Integration\nintegrations:\n  registry:\n    current_context_file: \"memory/current-context.md\"\n    \n  hooks:\n    on_context_switch: \"hooks/context-switch.md\"\n    \n  self_improving:\n    track_context_patterns: true\n    context_patterns_file: \"memory/self-improving/context-patterns.md\"\n","file_path":"C:/Users/andre/.openclaw/workspace/registry/contexts.yaml"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":3292,"output":1241,"cacheRead":124672,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":129205,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774476352091}}
