{"type":"message","id":"94fd1781","parentId":"97583b32","timestamp":"2026-03-25T23:49:24.653Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_uiACozvnbTs3wcF2dmGUJ4dr","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Verzeichnis: C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\second-brain\r\n\r\n\r\nMode                 LastWriteTime         Length Name                                                                 \r\n----                 -------------         ------ ----                                                                 \r\nd-----        26.03.2026     00:49                00-Dashboard                                                         \r\nd-----        26.03.2026     00:49                01-Sessions                                                          \r\n\r\n\r\n    Verzeichnis: C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\second-brain\\02-Areas\r\n\r\n\r\nMode                 LastWriteTime         Length Name                                                                 \r\n----                 -------------         ------ ----                                                                 \r\nd-----        26.03.2026     00:49                Decisions                                                            \r\nd-----        26.03.2026     00:49                Projects                                                             \r\n\r\n\r\n    Verzeichnis: C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\second-brain\\03-Resources\r\n\r\n\r\nMode                 LastWriteTime         Length Name                                                                 \r\n----                 -------------         ------ ----                                                                 \r\nd-----        26.03.2026     00:49                CodeBlocks                                                           \r\nd-----        26.03.2026     00:49                Dataview                                                             \r\n\r\n\r\n    Verzeichni