Decisions                                                            \r\nd-----        26.03.2026     00:49                Projects                                                             \r\n\r\n\r\n    Verzeichnis: C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\second-brain\\03-Resources\r\n\r\n\r\nMode                 LastWriteTime         Length Name                                                                 \r\n----                 -------------         ------ ----                                                                 \r\nd-----        26.03.2026     00:49                CodeBlocks                                                           \r\nd-----        26.03.2026     00:49                Dataview                                                             \r\n\r\n\r\n    Verzeichnis: C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\second-brain\r\n\r\n\r\nMode                 LastWriteTime         Length Name                                                                 \r\n----                 -------------         ------ ----                                                                 \r\nd-----        26.03.2026     00:49                04-Archive                                                           \r\nd-----        26.03.2026     00:49                05-Templates                                                         \r\n\r\n\r\n    Verzeichnis: C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\second-brain\\scripts\r\n\r\n\r\nMode                 LastWriteTime         Length Name                                                                 \r\n----                 -------------         ------ ----                                                                 \r\nd-----        26.03.2026     00:49                lib","cwd":"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774482564650}}
{"type":"message","id":"210beb68","parentId":"94fd1781","timestamp":"2026-03-25T23:50:03.513Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Gut, die Ordnerstruktur ist erstellt. Jetzt muss ich die wichtigsten Dateien erstellen:\n1. Dashboard.md\n2. Templates (Session, Decision, Project)\n3. Sync-Skript\n4. README\n\nIch werde diese nun erstellen.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Jetzt erstelle ich die Kern-Dateien:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_KhzpUDfL6xKPeIRcHDy45gQb","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Second Brain Dashboard\n\n```dataview\nTABLE WITHOUT ID\n  link(file.name) as Session,\n  dateformat(date, \"yyyy-MM-dd\") as Datum,\n  tokens as Tokens,\n  cost as Kosten,\n  status as Status\nFROM \"second-brain/01-Sessions\"\nSORT date DESC\nLIMIT 10\n```\n\n## 📊 Statistiken\n\n### Gesamt\n- **Sessions:** `=length(this.file.inlinks)`\n- **Entscheidungen:** `=length(filter(file.inlinks, (f) => contains(f.path, \"Decisions\")))`\n- **Projekte:** `=length(filter(file.inlinks, (f) => contains(f.path, \"Projects\")))`\n\n### Token-Usage (letzte 30 Tage)\n```dataview\nTABLE sum(tokens) as \"Gesamt Tokens\"\nFROM \"second-brain/01-Sessions\"\nWHERE date >= date(today) - dur(30 days)\nGROUP BY dateformat(date, \"yyyy-MM\") as Monat\n```\n\n## 🔴 Offene TODOs\n```dataview\nTASK\nFROM \"second-brain\"\nWHERE !completed\nAND contains(text, \"TODO\")\nSORT file.name ASC\n```\n\n## 🤔 Unentschiedene Entscheidungen\n```dataview\nTABLE status as Status, priority as Priorität\nFROM \"second-brain/02-Areas/Decisions\"\nWHERE status = \"Proposed\"\nSORT priority ASC\n```\n\n## 📈 Projekt-Fortschritt\n```dataview\nTABLE progress as Fortschritt, status as Status\nFROM \"second-brain/02-Areas/Projects\"\nSORT file.name ASC\n```\n\n## 🔗 Schnellzugriff\n- [[MOC-Framework|Framework Übersicht]]\n- [[01-Sessions/|Alle Sessions]]\n- [[02-Areas/Decisions/|Entscheidungen]]\n- [[02-Areas/Projects/|Projekte]]\n- [[03-Resources/|Ressourcen]]\n\n## 📝 Letzte Änderungen\n```dataview\nLIST\nFROM \"second-brain\"\nSORT file.mtime DESC\nLIMIT 5\n```\n","file_path":"C:/Users/andre/.openclaw/workspace/second-brain/00-Dashboard/Dashboard.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_wMeYzOoMVsYp87aocF5JrH0P","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ndate: {{date:YYYY-MM-DD}}\ntime: {{date:HH:mm}}\nsession_id: {{date:YYYYMMDDHHmmss}}\nagent: andrew-main\nuser: parzival\ntokens_in: 0\ntokens_out: 0\ncost: 0.0000\nstatus: active\ntags: []\nrelated_sessions: []\ndecisions: []\nprojects: []\n---\n\n# Session {{date:YYYY-MM-DD}}-{{date:HHmm}}\n\n## Zusammenfassung\n{{Zusammenfassung der Session}}\n\n## Getroffene Entscheidungen\n- [ ] Entscheidung 1 → [[ADR-XXX|Details]]\n\n## Offene TODOs\n- [ ] Task 1\n- [ ] Task 2\n\n## Wichtige Code-Blöcke\n```\n{{Code-Beispiele}}\n```\n\n## Erkenntnisse\n{{Key Learnings}}\n\n## Verknüpfungen\n- Vorherige: [[Session-XXX]]\n- Verwandt: [[Session-YYY]]\n\n---\n\n## Metadaten\n- **Start:** {{date:YYYY-MM-DD}} {{date:HH:mm}}\n- **Ende:** \n- **Dauer:** \n- **Modell:** kimi-coding/k2p5\n- **Thinking:** {{thinking_level}}\n","file_path":"C:/Users/andre/.openclaw/workspace/second-brain/05-Templates/Session-Template.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_DtK4qGOHJW9xyf3yHCmKlJ3H","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ndate: {{date:YYYY-MM-DD}}\nadr_id: ADR-{{sequence:001}}\ntitle: {{Titel der Entscheidung}}\nstatus: Proposed  # Proposed | Accepted | Deprecated\npriority: Medium   # Low | Medium | High | Critical\narea: {{Bereich}}\ntags: [adr, decision]\n---\n\n# ADR-{{sequence:001}}: {{Titel}}\n\n## Kontext\n{{Was ist das Problem? Welche Optionen wurden in Betracht gezogen?}}\n\n## Entscheidung\n{{Was wurde entschieden?}}\n\n## Konsequenzen\n\n### Positiv ✅\n- \n- \n\n### Negativ ⚠️\n- \n- \n\n## Alternativen\n| Option | Pros | Cons |\n|--------|------|------|\n| Option A | ... | ... |\n| Option B | ... | ... |\n\n## Verwandte Entscheidungen\n- [[ADR-XXX|Vorgänger]]\n- [[ADR-YYY|Abhängigkeit]]\n\n## Status-Verlauf\n- {{date:YYYY-MM-DD}}: Vorgeschlagen\n- {{date:YYYY-MM-DD}}: Akzeptiert\n","file_path":"C:/Users/andre/.openclaw/workspace/second-brain/05-Templates/Decision-Template.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_jGeyraFgr8eJDz7S2FDoKZZK","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\ndate: {{date:YYYY-MM-DD}}\nproject_id: PROJ-{{sequence:001}}\ntitle: {{Projektname}}\nstatus: Active  # Active | Paused | Completed | Cancelled\npriority: Medium\nprogress: 0\narea: {{Bereich}}\ntags: [project]\n---\n\n# PROJ-{{sequence:001}}: {{Projektname}}\n\n## Beschreibung\n{{Was ist das Ziel dieses Projekts?}}\n\n## Ziele\n- [ ] Ziel 1\n- [ ] Ziel 2\n- [ ] Ziel 3\n\n## Phasen\n| Phase | Status | Fortschritt |\n|-------|--------|-------------|\n| 1. Planning | ⬜ | 0% |\n| 2. Implementation | ⬜ | 0% |\n| 3. Testing | ⬜ | 0% |\n| 4. Deployment | ⬜ | 0% |\n\n## Sessions\n```dataview\nTABLE date as Datum, summary as Zusammenfassung\nFROM \"second-brain/01-Sessions\"\nWHERE contains(projects, \"PROJ-{{sequence:001}}\")\nSORT date DESC\n```\n\n## Entscheidungen\n```dataview\nTABLE status as Status\nFROM \"second-brain/02-Areas/Decisions\"\nWHERE contains(projects, \"PROJ-{{sequence:001}}\")\n```\n\n## Ressourcen\n- [[03-Resources/|Dokumentation]]\n- [[03-Resources/CodeBlocks/|Code-Beispiele]]\n\n## Notizen\n{{Projekt-Notizen}}\n","file_path":"C:/Users/andre/.openclaw/workspace/second-brain/05-Templates/Project-Template.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"kimi-k2-thinking","usage":{"input":988,"output":1712,"cacheRead":206848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":209548,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774482564661}}
