:** 90+\n- **Validierung:** 27/27 (100%)\n- **Version:** 1.3.0\n- **Status:** Production Ready\n\n## Verknüpfungen\n- Framework: [[../../README|Modular Agent Framework]]\n- Session Summary: [[C:/Users/andre/Documents/Andrew Openclaw/session-summary|Externe Zusammenfassung]]\n- Dashboard: [[00-Dashboard/Dashboard|Dashboard]]\n\n## Code-Blöcke extrahiert\n- [[03-Resources/CodeBlocks/|Siehe CodeBlocks]]\n\n## Tags\n#framework #implementation #ecc-integration #complete\n\"@\n\n$sbContent | Out-File \"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\second-brain\\01-Sessions\\Session-20260326.md\" -Encoding UTF8\nWrite-Host \"Session ins Second Brain kopiert ✅\" -ForegroundColor Green"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"kimi-k2-thinking","usage":{"input":184079,"output":759,"cacheRead":27904,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":212742,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774482762837}}
