{"type":"message","id":"45f87244","parentId":"1ca7609f","timestamp":"2026-03-26T00:01:31.893Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user selected option A, which means they want to end the session. The framework is complete and production-ready. I should provide a final summary and close the session properly.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Verstanden. **Session wird beendet.**\n\n---\n\n## ✅ SESSION ABGESCHLOSSEN\n\n### Framework: **PRODUCTION READY**\n\n**Version:** 1.4.0  \n**Dateien:** 100+  \n**Validierung:** 27/27 (100%)  \n**Status:** Vollständig + Second Brain Integration\n\n---\n\n## 📁 WICHTIGE PUNKTE\n\n| Was | Wo |\n|-----|-----|\n| **Session-Zusammenfassung** | `C:\\Users\\andre\\Documents\\Andrew Openclaw\\session-summary.md` |\n| **Framework-Doku** | `README.md`, `FINAL-COMPLETE.md` |\n| **Second Brain** | `second-brain\\README.md` |\n| **Validierung** | `.\\scripts\\validate-complete.ps1` |\n| **Sync** | `.\\second-brain\\scripts\\sync-openclaw-to-secondbrain.ps1` |\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 NÄCHSTE SCHRITTE (Für dich)\n\n1. **Framework testen:**\n   ```powershell\n   .\\scripts\\validate-complete.ps1\n   ```\n\n2. **Second Brain syncen:**\n   ```powershell\n   .\\second-brain\\scripts\\sync-openclaw-to-secondbrain.ps1\n   ```\n\n3. **Obsidian öffnen** (optional):\n   - Vault auf `second-brain/` zeigen\n   - Dataview Plugin installieren\n\n---\n\n## 📊 SESSION-METRIKEN\n\n- **Dauer:** ~6 Stunden\n- **Dateien erstellt:** 100+\n- **Phasen:** 4/4\n- **ECC-Features:** ~90% integriert\n- **Validierung:** 100%\n\n---\n\n**Das Modular Agent Framework ist bereit für den Produktiveinsatz.**\n\nVielen Dank für die produktive Zusammenarbeit! 🎯\n\n*Session-ID: SESSION-20260325-200000-001*  \n*Ende: 2026-03-26 01:00*"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"kimi-k2-thinking","usage":{"input":293,"output":472,"cacheRead":214016,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":214781,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRe