{"type":"message","id":"2421a717","parentId":"6a2659fc","timestamp":"2026-03-26T00:07:47.724Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_uUjdEoT7IneskgsJH0JyyYOu","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in C:/Users/andre/.openclaw/workspace/second-brain/scripts/sync-openclaw-to-secondbrain.ps1."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n 154 Write-Host \"  Sessions: $secondBrainRoot/01-Sessions/\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n 155 Write-Host \"  Projects: $secondBrainRoot/02-Areas/Projects/\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n 156 Write-Host \"  CodeBlocks: $secondBrainRoot/03-Resources/CodeBlocks/\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n 157 Write-Host \"  Dashboard: $secondBrainRoot/00-Dashboard/Dashboard.md\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n+158 \n+159 # Write timestamp for heartbeat tracking\n+160 $timestampFile = \"$secondBrainRoot/.last-sync\"\n+161 Get-Date -Format \"o\" | Out-File $timestampFile -Encoding UTF8\n+162 Write-Host \"  Timestamp: $timestampFile\" -ForegroundColor Gray","firstChangedLine":158},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774483667721}}
{"type":"message","id":"df151c27","parentId":"2421a717","timestamp":"2026-03-26T00:09:17.526Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Perfekt! Jetzt sollte ich dem Benutzer eine Zusammenfassung geben, was implementiert wurde.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## ✅ AUTOMATISCHE SYNC-KONFIGURATION IMPLEMENTIERT\n\n### 1. Hook (Sofort-Sync)\n**Datei:** `registry/hooks.yaml`\n\n```yaml\nsession:end:\n  post_actions:\n    - name: \"sync-second-brain\"\n      condition: \"session.duration_minutes > 10\"\n      enabled: true\n```\n\n**Funktioniert so:**\n- Nach jeder Session die länger als 10 Minuten dauert\n- Automatischer Sync ins Second Brain\n- Keine manuelle Aktion nötig\n\n---\n\n### 2. Heartbeat (Sicherheitsnetz)\n**Datei:** `HEARTBEAT.md`\n\n```yaml\ntasks:\n  - name: \"Second Brain Sync Check\"\n    schedule: \"daily\"\n    time: \"23:00\"\n    condition: \"new_sessions_since_last_sync OR last_sync_older_than_24h\"\n    action: \"sync-second-brain\"\n```\n\n**Funktioniert so:**\n- Jeden Abend um 23:00 prüft OpenClaw\n- Falls neue Sessions existieren oder letzter Sync >24h her\n- Automatischer Sync (silent - kein Noise)\n\n---\n\n### 3. Timestamp-Tracking\n**Datei:** `second-brain/.last-sync` (wird automatisch erstellt)\n\nDas Sync-Skript schreibt einen Zeitstempel, damit das Heartbeat weiß, wann zuletzt gesynct wurde.\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 ZUSAMMENFASSUNG\n\n| Auslöser | Wann | Aktion |\n|----------|------|--------|\n| **Hook** | Session Ende (>10min) | Sofort-Sync |\n| **Heartbeat** | Täglich 23:00 | Sync wenn nötig |\n| **Manuell** | Jederzeit | `.\\second-brain\\scripts\\sync-openclaw-to-secondbrain.ps1` |\n\n**Du musst nie wieder daran denken** - es passiert automatisch, aber du kannst jederzeit manuell syncen wenn du willst."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"kimi-k2-thinking","usage":{"input":148889,"output":484,"cacheRead":67072,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":216445,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774483667741}}
{"type":"message","id":"e58f3458","parentId":"df151c27","timestamp":"2026-03-26T00:09:17.742Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-03-26 01:05 GMT+1] kannst du etwas schreiben, dass wenn ich laptop starte immer terminal öffne und dann openclaw gateway start ausgeführt wird"}],"timestamp":1774483757724}}
{"type":"message","id":"887b1e9e","parentId":"e58f3458","timestamp":"2026-03-26T00:10:37.409Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to set up an automation so that when they start their laptop:\n1. Terminal opens automatically\n2. The command \"openclaw gateway start\" is executed\n\nThis is a Windows-specific automation task. I should provide solutions for:\n1. Creating a startup script/task\n2. Opening terminal automatically\n3. Running the openclaw command\n\nOptions:\n1. Windows Task Scheduler - Create a task that runs on logon\n2. Startup folder - Create a batch file or PowerShell script in the Startup folder\n3. Windows Service - More complex, probably overkill\n4. Registry Run key - Classic startup method\n\nThe easiest and most reliable would be:\n- Option 1: Task Scheduler (more control)\n- Option 2: Startup folder (simpler)\n\nI'll provide both options with clear instructions.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Ja, ich zeige dir mehrere Möglichkeiten für Windows:\n\n---\n\n## OPTION 1: Startup-Ordner (Einfachste)\n\n### 1. Batch-Datei erstellen"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_OnttNU129yJAAsILQGR6nCra","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"@echo off\necho Starting OpenClaw Gateway...\nstart wt.exe powershell.exe -Command \"openclaw gateway start; Write-Host 'Gateway gestartet. Druecke eine Taste...' -ForegroundColor Green; pause\"\n","file_path":"C:/Users/andre/AppData/Roaming/Microsoft/Windows/Start Menu/Programs/Startup/start-openclaw.bat"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"kimi-k2-thinking","usage":{"input":131563,"output":305,"cacheRead":84736,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":216604,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774483757739}}
