{"type":"message","id":"3f6661d9","parentId":"5c0c61f7","timestamp":"2026-03-26T00:11:55.187Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I created the batch file. Now let me provide the PowerShell alternative and Task Scheduler option as well.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **Fertig!** Die Batch-Datei liegt jetzt im Startup-Ordner.\n\n**Was passiert:**\n- Beim Laptop-Start öffnet sich automatisch Windows Terminal\n- Führt `openclaw gateway start` aus\n- Zeigt Erfolgsmeldung und wartet auf Tastendruck\n\n---\n\n## OPTION 2: PowerShell-Version (Besseres Terminal)\n\nFalls du lieber PowerShell direkt willst:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_Pk25D2FY51NvlipIDjTP4YrW","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# OpenClaw Gateway Auto-Start\n# Diese Datei liegt im Startup-Ordner und startet automatisch\n\nWrite-Host \"🚀 Starte OpenClaw Gateway...\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n\n# Prüfe ob Gateway läuft\n$status = openclaw gateway status 2>$null\n\nif ($status -match \"running|läuft\") {\n    Write-Host \"✅ Gateway läuft bereits\" -ForegroundColor Green\n} else {\n    Write-Host \"⏳ Starte Gateway...\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n    openclaw gateway start\n    \n    # Warte kurz und prüfe Status\n    Start-Sleep -Seconds 2\n    $newStatus = openclaw gateway status\n    \n    if ($newStatus -match \"running|läuft\") {\n        Write-Host \"✅ Gateway erfolgreich gestartet!\" -ForegroundColor Green\n    } else {\n        Write-Host \"❌ Fehler beim Starten\" -ForegroundColor Red\n    }\n}\n\nWrite-Host \"`nDruecke eine Taste zum Schliessen...\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n$null = $Host.UI.RawUI.ReadKey(\"NoEcho,IncludeKeyDown\")\n","file_path":"C:/Users/andre/AppData/Roaming/Microsoft/Windows/Start Menu/Programs/Startup/start-openclaw.ps1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"kimi-k2-thinking","usage":{"input":119924,"output":443,"cacheRead":96512,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":216879,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774483837433}}
