{"type":"message","id":"f96e1dcf","parentId":"1deea92a","timestamp":"2026-03-26T00:31:07.917Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_1fPszrq2GOeLHlZLzdu1L9iA","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Knowledge Curator Analysis\nVault: C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\second-brain\n\nFound 8 notes\n\nANALYSIS RESULTS\n===================\nTotal Notes: 8\nConnected: 5 (62.5 %)\nOrphaned: 3 (37.5 %)\nBroken Links: 24\n\nTOP 10 HUB NOTES\n\r\nname              backlinks\r\n----              ---------\r\nDashboard                 2\r\nProject-Template          1\r\nREADME                    1\r\nDecision-Template         0\r\nSession-Template          0\r\nMOC-Startseite            0\r\nSession-20260326          0\r\nProjects-Overview         0\r\n\r\n\r\n\nORPHANED NOTES\n\r\nname              size recommendation reason                  \r\n----              ---- -------------- ------                  \r\nProjects-Overview  636 REVIEW         Orphaned but has content\r\nDecision-Template  757 REVIEW         Orphaned but has content\r\nSession-Template   776 REVIEW         Orphaned but has content\r\n\r\n\r\n\nRECOMMENDATIONS\nDELETE (0 notes):\n\nREVIEW (3 notes):\n  - 02-Areas\\Projects\\Projects-Overview.md\n  - 05-Templates\\Decision-Template.md\n  - 05-Templates\\Session-Template.md\n\nReport saved: C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\second-brain/../analysis-report-20260326-0131.json\n\nAnalysis complete!"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1129,"aggregated":"Knowledge Curator Analysis\nVault: C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\second-brain\n\nFound 8 notes\n\nANALYSIS RESULTS\n===================\nTotal Notes: 8\nConnected: 5 (62.5 %)\nOrphaned: 3 (37.5 %)\nBroken Links: 24\n\nTOP 10 HUB NOTES\n\r\nname              backlinks\r\n----              ---------\r\nDashboard                 2\r\nProject-Template          1\r\nREADME                    1\r\nDecision-Template         0\r\nSession-Template          0\r\nMOC-Startseite            0\r\nSession-20260326          0\r\nProjects-Overview         0\r\n\r\n\r\n\nORPHANED NOTES\n\r\nname              size recommendation reason                  \r\n----              ---- -------------- ------                  \r\nProjects-Overview  636 REVIEW         Orphaned but has content\r\nDecision-Template  757 REVIEW         Orphaned but has content\r\nSession-Template   776 REVIEW         Orphaned but has content\r\n\r\n\r\n\nRECOMMENDATIONS\nDELETE (0 notes):\n\nREVIEW (3 notes):\n  - 02-Areas\\Projects\\Projects-Overview.md\n  - 05-Templates\\Decision-Template.md\n  - 05-Templates\\Session-Template.md\n\nReport saved: C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\second-brain/../analysis-report-20260326-0131.json\n\nAnalysis complete!","cwd":"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774485067914}}
{"type":"message","id":"958b6464","parentId":"f96e1dcf","timestamp":"2026-03-26T00:31:25.920Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Perfekt! Die Analyse läuft. Ich zeige die Ergebnisse übersichtlich.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## 📊 VAULT ANALYSE ERGEBNIS\n\n### Übersicht\n| Metrik | Wert |\n|--------|------|\n| **Gesamt Notizen** | 8 |\n| **Verbunden** | 5 (62.5%) ✅ |\n| **Verwaist (Orphans)** | 3 (37.5%) ⚠️ |\n| **Kaputte Links** | 24 ❌ |\n\n---\n\n### 🔗 Top Hub Notizen\n| Notiz | Backlinks |\n|-------|-----------|\n| Dashboard | 2 |\n| Project-Template | 1 |\n| README | 1 |\n\n---\n\n### ⚠️ Verwaiste Notizen (3)\n\n| Notiz | Größe | Empfehlung |\n|-------|-------|------------|\n| Projects-Overview | 636 Bytes | REVIEW |\n| Decision-Template | 757 Bytes | REVIEW |\n| Session-Template | 776 Bytes | REVIEW |\n\n**Grund:** Templates haben natürlich keine Backlinks (werden kopiert, nicht verlinkt)\n\n---\n\n### 🔴 24 Kaputte Links\n\nDie meisten sind wahrscheinlich **Template-Platzhalter** wie `[[Session-XXX]]` oder `[[ADR-001]]`.\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 EMPFEHLUNGEN\n\n### Sofort:\n1. **Templates markieren** - Als `type: template` kennzeichnen (dann werden sie nicht als Orphans gewertet)\n\n2. **Kaputte Links fixen**:\n   ```powershell\n   # In Templates: Platzhalter klarer markieren\n   [[Session-{{ID}}]] → {{Session-Link}}\n   ```\n\n### Optional:\n3. **Verbindungen schaffen**:\n   - MOC-Startseite mit Projects-Overview verlinken\n   - Dashboard mit allen Templates verlinken\n\n---\n\n## 💡 WISSENSWERT\n\nDein Second Brain ist noch **jung** (8 Notizen). Die \"Orphans\" sind **Templates** - das ist normal und gewollt!\n\n**Der Knowledge Curator funktioniert!** Sobald du mehr Sessions hast, wird die Analyse aussagekräftiger.\n\n**Report gespeichert:** `analysis-report-20260326-0131.json`\n\nSoll ich:\n- A) Die Templates als \"nicht-orphan\" kennzeichnen?\n- B) Verbindungen von der MOC-Startseite zu allen Templates schaffen?\n- C) Die kaputten Links in den Templates korrigieren?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"kimi-k2-thinking","usage":{"input":586,"output":573,"cacheRead":219648,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":220807,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774485067928}}
