{"type":"message","id":"0d5429a7","parentId":"8a793119","timestamp":"2026-03-26T01:15:04.747Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Ah! There it is! The file is showing corrupted characters - the German umlauts (ü, ä, ö) are being displayed as garbled characters. This is an encoding issue, not Chinese/Mandarin.\n\nThe user is seeing corrupted UTF-8 characters that look like Chinese/gibberish because the terminal or Obsidian is not reading the UTF-8 encoding properly. The special German characters (ü, ö, ä, ß) are being misinterpreted.\n\nI need to explain that these are encoding issues with German special characters, not Chinese text.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"## ❌ ACHTUNG: ENCODING-PROBLEM ENTDECKT!\n\nDas sind **keine chinesischen Zeichen** - das sind **kaputte deutsche Umlaute**!\n\n**Was passiert:**\n- `ü` → wird zu `�\"` oder ähnlichem Müll\n- `ä` → wird zu `�\"` \n- `ö` → wird zu `�\"`\n\nDas ist ein **UTF-8 Encoding Problem**, kein Chinesisch!\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 WARUM PASSIERT DAS?\n\nDie Dateien sind korrekt als **UTF-8** gespeichert, aber:\n- Windows Terminal zeigt sie manchmal falsch an\n- Obsidian erwartet möglicherweise **UTF-8 with BOM**\n- Oder dein Editor hat falsches Encoding\n\n---\n\n## ✅ LÖSUNG\n\n### Für Obsidian:\n1. **Obsidian öffnen**\n2. **Settings → Files and Links**\n3. **Default encoding auf UTF-8 setzen**\n\n### Oder: Dateien reparieren"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_qRVJxtJ8L4i2yKGvYpcvx8cT","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Schreibe eine Datei neu mit BOM (Byte Order Mark) für bessere Windows-Kompatibilität\n$content = Get-Content \"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\second-brain\\README.md\" -Raw\n# Speichere mit UTF8-BOM\n$utf8Bom = New-Object System.Text.UTF8Encoding $true\n[System.IO.File]::WriteAllText(\"C:\\Users\\andre\\.openclaw\\workspace\\second-brain\\README-fixed.md\", $content, $utf8Bom)\nWrite-Host \"Datei mit UTF-8 BOM gespeichert\" -ForegroundColor Green"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"kimi-k2-thinking","usage":{"input":821,"output":499,"cacheRead":231168,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":232488,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774487691027}}
